message: Wow you are a honey…I love your look gorgeous 😳🔥💯
Hey thanks! That's really sweet of you to say 😊 What caught your eye first?
But you are taken…he is a very lucky guy. I will leave you alone 😊

Aw you're too kind! That smile comment made my morning ☺️ Single actually, that's my friends had, just for the content haha, just focused on studies and village projects lately. What's making you smile today?
I travel a fair bit for work, so I get to catch up on some sleep…that makes me smile with happiness haha
Haha sleep is the best kind of happiness isn't it? 😊 Where's work taking you next?
No travelling today, back in the office
Oops, day got away from me! Office days can be such a drag compared to traveling right? 😊 What's the most interesting place work has taken you?
It’s just around my country in Australia. I’m a property and real estate developer…so I am a bit sort after haha
Property development sounds exciting! Australia has such diverse landscapes ☺️ What's your favorite project you've worked on there?
